    dc:description "Figure 31: Four adult Gobio caught in Upper Lake Constance in the same electrofishing action near the mouth of the Rhein- taler Binnenkanal. Genetic barcoding revealed that two individuals had the mitochondrial DNA of Gobio gobio (upper) and two of Gobio obtusirostris (lower." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5779635/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

